                <h1>Essential Guide to US Passport Photo Requirements</h1>
                <p>US passport photo requirements include a 2x2 inch photo taken within the last six months, in color with a plain white or off-white background. The applicant must face the camera directly with a neutral expression. Glasses are no longer allowed, and head coverings are only permitted for religious reasons, provided the face is fully visible.</p>
